      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve kept it garage-parked and babied it since day one\u2014it's spotless inside and out! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 43500.0,
