      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the zenith of BMW's naturally aspirated era. The S54 3.2L straight-six features a high-pressure Double VANOS system and six individual throttle bodies, producing an exhilarating 333hp with a razor-sharp throttle response. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual and a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential, the drivetrain is in peerless condition. The chassis has undergone a proactive subframe reinforcement and a full suspension refresh with OE bushings. From the pristine undercarriage to the factory-spec paint depth, this vehicle remains mechanically and aesthetically flawless, offering a pure, unadulterated driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
