    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s specimen, preserved in a state that rivals its original showroom debut. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that remains entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains that distinct new-car aroma; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and every digital interface functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records documenting its pampered life in a climate-controlled garage. The engine bay is immaculate, and the drive is whisper-quiet yet responsive, reflecting its low mileage and fastidious upkeep. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
